{"id": 1415, "genre": 1001, "title": "现如今你为什么还会去 KTV？", "description": "以前一起唱周杰伦的朋友都不在身边了，但新的二次元同好 or 喊麦爱好者好像又为 KTV 找到了新玩法，所以你最近一次去 KTV 是为啥？（题图来自：Nickola Nickolov）", "record_count": 3537, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/201612280003549G3XTemB2sLbD8iI.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-12-30T03:00:44Z", "options": [{"id": 149504, "content": "我不去，因为穷！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 879967}, {"id": 150016, "content": "同学聚聚会才去！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 834136}, {"id": 151808, "content": "发泄呗，有好的释放，才能有好的生活态度", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 832416}, {"id": 149249, "content": "夏天的时候是因为那里空调开的足，然后打牌！", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 103310}, {"id": 149505, "content": "KTV是另一个继续喝酒的场所……", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 870561}, {"id": 149761, "content": "一个廉价的房间，顺带可以唱歌", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 886886}, {"id": 149506, "content": "跟朋友去", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 871567}, {"id": 152066, "content": "什么是KTV？", "image": "img/option/option_pic/20170109131959K13zJQXR6LdUWlgYo.jpg", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 776361}, {"id": 149251, "content": "一起唱周杰伦的朋友还在?", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1035814}, {"id": 149507, "content": "偶尔需要去宣泄下自己的情绪", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 879251}, {"id": 149252, "content": "都想不起最近什么时候去的了？", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 668553}, {"id": 149509, "content": "没话聊也不尴尬", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 55455}, {"id": 150533, "content": "去放松心情，是个发泄情绪的好地方", "image": "img/option/option/20170104193614TMBX8qPoKevuli0n", "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 890674}, {"id": 149254, "content": "最近听了一些不错的歌 分享一下", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 790765}, {"id": 149766, "content": "一个人练歌，开心", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 868894}, {"id": 149511, "content": "不会去吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 885954}, {"id": 151815, "content": "for fun with my friend", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 896785}, {"id": 149256, "content": "想唱就唱，唱得漂亮", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 878428}, {"id": 151305, "content": "只是一群老友找一个不被打扰的空间调低音量小酌聊天而已", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 893763}, {"id": 149770, "content": "便宜", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 771279}, {"id": 150026, "content": "聚会没啥玩的，KTV老少皆宜，都去吼一吼。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 887514}, {"id": 150538, "content": "哈哈", "image": "img/option/option/20170104195430tGLFKQe7liaR3zWU", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 614267}, {"id": 149259, "content": "凑热闹啊\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 734792}, {"id": 149515, "content": "最近一次去……\n是什么时候的事?", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 885961}, {"id": 149771, "content": "已经过了去KTV 的年纪了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 887218}, {"id": 149260, "content": "team building", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 852595}, {"id": 149516, "content": "所有歌曲都能变成大合唱。我不去。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 855503}, {"id": 149261, "content": "回忆吧～对爱(⑉°з°)-♡的记忆！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 885142}, {"id": 149517, "content": "和当年唱周杰伦的小伙伴们叙旧", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 142377}, {"id": 149774, "content": "呐喊，彷徨", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 887222}, {"id": 149263, "content": "去唱歌，听别人说我唱的好", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 421057}, {"id": 149519, "content": "欣赏朋友们魅力的一面", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 710854}, {"id": 151567, "content": "朋友", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 895285}, {"id": 149264, "content": "想去唱歌", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 763836}, {"id": 149520, "content": "好长时间都没去过了， 就算了去了也不会唱， 没有对的人，我是永远不会开口……", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 886010}, {"id": 149776, "content": "好友，大酌", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 759944}, {"id": 151568, "content": "包厢里回响好", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 349453}, {"id": 273681, "content": "我就在KTV做策划工作，你以为我愿意吗？", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1300677}, {"id": 149265, "content": "越来越觉得KTV很多歌曲我都不会唱了！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 823837}, {"id": 152593, "content": "朋友拉去的好吧，不想去的好吧，没办法的啦好吧！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 900996}, {"id": 149266, "content": "告诉我在后半夜还有哪个娱乐场所适合我这个底薪屌丝去？", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 713394}, {"id": 152338, "content": "很簡單因為想唱歌 最近一次因為朋友失戀陪她宣洩！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 898745}, {"id": 149523, "content": "嗨啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 886015}, {"id": 149779, "content": "酒后必去", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 887238}, {"id": 149524, "content": "打发时间", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 886012}, {"id": 150292, "content": "唱歌 每错 就是单纯喜欢唱歌 连酒都不点就喝饮料", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 814636}, {"id": 149269, "content": "唱歌好听喜欢去KTV炫耀难道要大声说吗？?", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 198868}, {"id": 149525, "content": "五音不全，去了基本就是把人带跑调\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 827319}, {"id": 149270, "content": "喝醉了找个不打扰别人也不会被打的地方耍酒疯砸酒瓶子玩", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 567071}, {"id": 149526, "content": "早就不想去了，硬逼着去的", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 441858}]}